examples.en: The moon was a silvery orb.
Silvery light reflected off the water.
Below were the silvery lakes, above were the snowy peaks.
examples.ru: Внизу сверкали серебристые озёра, вверху белели снежные вершины.

examples.en: The leaves are green on top and silvery on the underside.
examples.ru: Сверху эти листья зелёные, а снизу — серебристые.

examples.en: Sage leaves have a silvery cast.
The carpet had a silvery sheen to it.
